title: Interlaboratory Study
text: aim ILS package detect laboratories provide consistent results, working simultaneously different test materials, perspective Univariate Data Analysis Functional Data Analysis (FDA). ILS package estimates Mandel’s h k univariate statistics, based ASTM E691 ISO 5725-2 standards, identify laboratories provide significantly different results. Cochran Grubbs tests evaluate presence outliers also available. addition, Analysis Variance (ANOVA) techniques provided, including Tukey F tests evaluate differences means corresponding test variable. One novelties package incorporation tools perform ILS functional data analysis approach. Accordingly, functional nature data obtained experimental techniques corresponding analytical chemistry, applied physics engineering applications (spectra, thermograms, sensor signals, among others) taking account implementing functional extensions Mandel’s h k statistics. purpose, ILS package also estimates functional statistics H(t) K(t), well dH y dK test statistic, used evaluate repeatability reproducibility hypotheses critical ch ck values estimated using bootstrap algorithm.
